# Build-context filter for mayhem/Dockerfile ONLY (BuildKit uses <Dockerfile>.dockerignore in preference
# to the context-root .dockerignore). Unlike upstream's root .dockerignore, this KEEPS .git so the commit
# image carries full history (SPEC §6.2 item 2). Prune only local build cruft.
**/__pycache__
**/.DS_Store
**/node_modules
